        <p>The Service is an administrative technology tool. It does NOT provide and is NOT a substitute for:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>(a) Legal advice from a licensed attorney;</li>
          <li>(b) Real estate advice from a licensed broker;</li>
          <li>(c) Financial or tax advice from a licensed accountant or financial advisor;</li>
          <li>(d) Title or escrow services from a licensed provider;</li>
